text: Manuel García (born 20 March 1964) is a former cyclist from Guam. He competed in four events at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1964 births Category:Living people Category:Guamanian male cyclists Category:Olympic cyclists of Guam Category:Cyclists at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:American track cyclists Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
